s, all to the serenade of the recently developed synthesizer. Shapiro maps out these converging influences, as well as disco\'s cultural antecedents in Europe, looks at the history of DJing, explores the mainstream disco craze at it\'s apex, and details the long shadow cast by disco\'s performers and devotees on today\'s musical landscape. One part cultural study, one part urban history, and one part glitter-pop confection, &quot;Turn the Beat Around&quot; is the most comprehensive study of the Me Generation to date.<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"11900759091117588115\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'18_book_883815\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"1wuZtJ1uRAwJXp+dMCIaSaGk8F76TxcL6/Q64k3pfrnBa0QIvJhrYxGr/DqhwQj8WYehMYjWebEQXq4xo1oiLw==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"883815\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"18_book_883815\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_home_module\" id=\"from_home_module\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"ref\" id=\"ref\" value=\"\" class=\"wtrLeftUpRef\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"existing_review\" id=\"existing_review\" value=\"false\" class=\"wtrExisting\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_origin\" id=\"book_origin\" value=\"related_works\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"page_url\" id=\"page_url\" value=\"/book/show/86856.A_Cook_s_Tour\" />\n<button class=\'wtrToRead\' type=\'submit\'>\n<span class=\